abstract: >-
  This repository stores metadata templates in use at
  SciLifeLab, organized according to data type. It focuses
  on capturing technical metadata, i.e. metadata about the
  experiments and technologies used to generate the data it
  describes.

  The metadata templates are designed to be compatible with
  metadata requirements from established data end
  repositories for a given data type or research area. 
